snippet.title: NEW | Sniper Elite 3 |  Teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the first teaser trailer for Sniper Elite 3. The game is coming to PS4 and PS3 later this year.

Can you stop a super weapon with the power to crush any Allied force? Jump into a new campaign in North Africa, 1942.
